        <h2>About Euphoriq</h2>
        <p>
            Ubong Peter Asangsusung, known professionally as Euphoriq, is a Nigerian singer, songwriter, guitarist,
            recording and performing artist. He began his music career by performing live acoustic music weekly on the
            Hit breakfast show at Hit95.9FM Calabar. He moved on to performing at private parties, concerts, clubs, open
            mic sessions, listening rooms, and music festivals. He has also been a contestant on The Voice Nigeria
            Season 4, Covers Africa Season 2.
        </p>
        <p>
            Known for a crispy, raspy yet soothing voice texture, his repertoire consists of an acoustic variety of
            pop, rock, afro rock, afro soul, and classics. Currently, he is working on an EP project that would be his
            first official body of work.
        </p>
